er *[[Anu Viheriäranta]] – ballet dancer *[[Antti Viitikko]] – badminton player *[[Janne Virtanen]] – world's strongest man champion *[[Emil Väre]] – wrestler, two Olympic gold medals (1885–1974) *[[Verner Weckman]] – wrestler, two Olympic gold medals (1882–1968) *[[Kurt Wires]] – rower, two Olympic gold medals (1919–1991) {{div col end}}
